Public Administrator of New York County, as Administrator of the Estate of Salvatore Frieri, Deceased, Respondent, v. Vincente Gallo et al., Appellants.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the respondent. No opinion. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, M. M. Frank, Valente and Stevens, JJ.
